        "525": {
          "vnum": 525,
          "name": "Lowode Clearing",
          "description": "Tendrils of steam rise up from cracks in the ground here among the Lowode hills. The area appears to have been recently filled in with fresh soil. Small saplings and sprouts struggle for life and light within the loosely packed, mineral-rich earth. Paths lead north and south.",
