        "2704": {
          "vnum": 2704,
          "name": "In the Forest",
          "description": "Great gnarled roots writhe upward from the ground here among some of the tallest of the ancient redwoods, which continue their prevalence despite the steadily rising terrain to the east. A thin trail begins here, working its way eastward, and eventually up along the ridge. Off to the southwest arcs a collosal root, framing a passage into the forested basin. The power of the ocean gradually subsides.",
