          "name": "In the Forest",
          "description": "Leaves cascade in a ceaseless dance from the ancient forest trees about you here, deep within the basin. A slight breeze brushes against your cheek, flowing off the surface of a murky, stillwater lake. The shore lies to your north, and a passable trail winds westward, marked by a rotting sign, half obscured by leaves and ivy.",
