          "name": "Inside a Small Cave",
          "description": "Unnaturally smooth and rounded walls make up the interior of this small cave, hidden from outside view by creeping foliage upon the ever rising terrain. The cave dead-ends abruptly, a stinking pool of fetid water filled with gryphon's dung and victim's bone at its farthest corner.",
