        "454": {
          "vnum": 454,
          "name": "Hidden Sanctum",
          "description": "This tiny room is cleverly hidden below the holy altar, a private place to study holy texts; and, more recently it would seem, books of a much darker origin. Writings on disease and necromancy line a small shelf on one wall, while others are stacked on the meager desk. A ring of pale, translucent mushrooms grows here, faintly luminous. Pure white blossoms grow here, radiating a soft divine light.",
